Preconditions:
- The input word is a string consisting of uppercase English letters.
- The length of the word is at least 2 and at most 300.

Postconditions:
- The method returns an integer representing the minimum total distance to type the given word using only two fingers.
- The initial positions of the two fingers are considered free and do not count towards the total distance.
- The two fingers do not have to start at the first letter or the first two letters.